---
title: Cherry Balsamic Bavette Steak with Herby Fingerling Potatoes & Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Your steak dinner as you know it has officially been fancified with French flavors. Le menu: Seared bavette cuts drizzled with a savory-sweet pan sauce. For the sides, there are fingerling potatoes roasted with herbes de Provence, tender Brussels sprouts, and tangy, balsamic-roasted onion. Beat that, Parisian bistros!
